We’ve been told COVID vaccines saved millions of lives—but new research shreds that claim, suggesting the real number is far lower and that aggressive mandates were built on shaky science. From billion-dollar incentives for pediatricians to outright lies about risk and benefit, the pandemic exposed a system where profit and control outweighed truth. This is about more than vaccines—it’s about the web of government, corporate, and media interests that thrived while ordinary people paid the price.
